snippet.title: Rock of Ages 2: Bigger & Boulder - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Get ready to rock n’ roll! Rock of Ages 2: Bigger & Boulder is available now on the Nintendo Switch, and those who pick up the game within the first 2 weeks of launch will receive the Binding of Isaac DLC for free. It's time to put prominent historical features between a rock and a hard place! 

Learn more about Rock of Ages 2: Bigger & Boulder http://www.rockofages2.com

#NintendoSwitch #RockofAges2
